<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Privacy Policy | The Learning Sphere</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --text: #111111;
      --muted: #666666;
      --accent: #000000;
      --border: #e0e0e0;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .date {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      padding-left: 10px;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    a:hover {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="date">Effective Date: <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong></p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy explains how The Learning Sphere collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our platform.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Personal Info:</strong> Name, email, phone, profile image, etc.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, clicks, etc.</li>
      <li><strong>Device Info:</strong> Browser, IP address, OS.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To personalize your learning experience</li>
      <li>To improve our platform and features</li>
      <li>To contact you with updates and support</li>
      <li>To prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance functionality and gather analytics. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We never sell your data. We may share with trusted service providers (like email or payment processors) under strict confidentiality agreements.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored securely. We use encryption, secure servers, and regular monitoring. However, no system is 100% immune to breaches.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your data</li>
      <li>Edit or delete your account</li>
      <li>Opt-out of non-essential communications</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may link to other websites or use third-party tools (like Google Analytics). Their privacy policies may differ.</p>

    <h2>9. Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>
    <p>We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13. If we learn of such data, we will delete it promptly.</p>

    <h2>10. Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as our platform evolves. Check this page regularly. Major updates will be notified via email.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@learningsphere.com">privacy@learningsphere.com</a></p>

    <footer>
      &copy; {{year}} The Learning Sphere. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
